Tumblr Images Downloader ( TID for short) gets all the images of a given tumblr blog and saves them on your computer.

Download from here : https://github.com/downloads/aviatrix/tumblr-downloader/tumblr-downloader.zip
or just go to the downloads section..

For programers : feel free to poke with the code.
